"the LINSTOR deployment.\n"
"\n"
"Here is an example of mapping an Exos Pool in Exos enclosure Alpha to two Satellite nodes:\n"
"\n"
"[bash]\n"
"----\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"linstor_pool_nameは、LINSTOR デプロイメントに対して(ほぼ)任意の\n"
